# text = Sesoh ne ni singkil khombongen khaje malet susah mendapat ken ketadingen sang gukhu kakhene enggo bue jeme luakh akhi khoh me singkil amin hendak me daun me sang gukhu Ni khumah gukhu mbelin kalakdi medaun khut tekun te sabakh sang khaje me matuhi kekhine pesakhaten si ni pido oleh dukun mebane
# text[en] = Arriving at Singkil, the King's entourage had no difficulty finding where the Master Teacher lived, because many people from outside the area came to Singkil to seek treatment from the Master Teacher. In the home of the Master Teacher, they sought treatment with diligence and patience, and the king complied with all the requirements requested by the Shaman for him.
# text[id] = Sesampainya di Singkil rombongan Raja ini tidak susah mendapatkan kediaman sang Guru, karena sudah banyak orang dari luar datang ke Singkil Cuma hendak berobat ke sang Guru.  Dirumah Guru Mbelin mereka berobat dengan tekun dan sabar, sang raja mematuhi segala persyaratan yang diminta oleh dukun kepadanya. 
