# newpar
# text = Namun pengkikhaen pengulu mude meleset Sang khaje te bekhune engo balik me kute ne ni kekhan khut wajah mesekhi-sekhi te siap menjabut saat-saat si Nitimai soh Pige bulan kemudian bekhune mengandung bage si ni kateken si dukun Senanglah kikhene sang khaje memege kabakh bahwe sang bekhune enggo mengandung sekalak anak
# text[en] = But Pengulu Mude's understanding of the situation was far from the truth. The king and his wife had returned to the town in Engkeran with beaming faces and were ready to welcome the expected time to arrive. A few months later the wife was carrying a child like what the shaman had said. The king was so happy to hear the news that his wife was pregnant with a child.
# text[id] = Sang raja dan istri telah kembali ke Kuta-nya di Engkeran dengan wajah berseri-seri dan siap menyambut saat-saat yang dinantikan tiba. Beberapa bulan kemudian istrinya mengandung seperti yang dikatakan si dukun. Senanglah kiranya sang raja mendengar kabar bahwa sang istri sudah mengandung seorang anak.
