# newpar
# text = Pade suatu wakhi Si Layakh mengembale ni deleng iye malot nange panganen kakhene enggo hancukh iye gakhami buah-buahen ni deleng Malet sengaje iye jumpe khut ninik-ninik gakhami seban tutung se enggo ninik edi mulungi seban ne iye buet ken wakhan mejolokh untuk mekhakut sejumlah seban si iye gakhami semange edi Begedi si ninik menakhik wakhan edi malet sengaje tededoh Si Layakh tekhus ni tahan Si Layakh lah ni takhik balik oleh ninik te nitahan ne kane tule te setekhusne
# text[en] = One day when Si Layakh was shepherding in the mountains, he did not have clothing because his clothes had already been completely worn out when he was searching for fruit in the wilderness. Unintentionally, he met with some grandmother firewood scavengers. After one of the grandmothers collected her firewood, she took a creeping root to tie the wood that she had just found together. As soon as the grandmother pulled the root up, Si Layakh accidentally stepped on it and it was held down by Si Layakh, the grandmother pulled on the root again and it was held down again and so on.
# text[id] = Pada Suatu hari Si layakh mengembala di gunung, dia tidak lagi mempunyai pakaian karena sudah hancur dia mencari buah-buahan di hutan.  Tanpa sengaja dia berjumpa dengan nenek-nenek pencari kayu bakar, setelah nenek itu mengumpulkan kayu bakarnya, dia mengambil akar menjalar untuk mengikat sejumlah kayu yang ia cari sebelumnya. Begitu si nenek menarik akar itu, tanpa sengaja terinjak oleh Si Layakh, lalu ditahan olehnya Si layakh,  ditarik kembali oleh si nenek dan ditahannya pula lagi dan seterusnya.
