# newpar
# text = Si ninik khut mate kabukh mengato ise sosok si menganggu wakhi ende bage manusie tapi malet mebaju bage manusie malot memasakhakat Tekhus si ninik dempik Woi si ni hadih apekah kao manusie atau jin Te kao manusie ciduhken lah dikhimu Te kao jin kae si kao pido bangku akhi
# text[en] = The grandmother with blurry vision tried to see who it was that was upsetting her today. He looked like a human, but was not dressed like a human (not following Shari'ah law). Then the grandmother shouted: "Hey you over there....are you a human or a jinn? If you are human show yourself. If you are a jinn, what do you want from me?"
# text[id] = Si nenek dengan mata agak rabun berupaya melihat siapa sosok yang mengganggu hari ini, seperti manusia, tapi tidak berpakaian selayaknya manusia (tidak bersyari’at). Lalu si nenek berteriak: “hai yang disana… apakah kau manusia atau jin? jika kamu manusia tunjukanlah diri kamu jika kamu jin apa yang engkau inginkan dariku?”
