# text = Keluakhge khaje Natam bakhu pelin menikmati suasane khumah bakhu khumah si megah ni banding ken khumah-khumah lain ne Namun keyamanen khumah bakhu edi tekhusik khut dempiken-dempiken pakhau akhi sahung khumah Se engo ni ato me sahung khumah tekhyate engo cindekh tegak sebuah manuk keluki delaki dempik-dempik kekhas se sikel me mekhe sebuah petande kabakh malot mejile enggo kabakh edi akhi dape asal ne
# text[en] = The King of Natam's family had just begun to enjoy the niceties of having a new home, a very large and beautiful house compared to other houses. But the comfort of the new house was disrupted by the hoarse screams from the roof of the house. After looking at the roof of the house, it turned out that there was a male eagle standing upright and screaming loudly as if giving a sign of bad news. Where did that news come from?
# text[id] = Keluarga Raja Natam baru saja menikmati suasana rumah baru, rumah yang sangat megah dibandingkan rumah-rumah lainnya, namun kenyamanan rumah baru itu terusik dengan teriakan-teriakan parau dari atap rumah.  Setelah diliat ketap rumah ternyata telah berdiri tegak seekor burung elang jantan berteriak-teriak keras seakan memberi suatu petanda kabar buruk.  sudah kabar itu dari mana asalnya.
