# newpar
# text = Kane meyusullah sekelompok cut pengawal kekhajaen Natam untuk meyusul khombongen khaje ngkhan Tepat amin sesohne ni pulo biang idah akhi tekhuh jukhang sesosok manusie si tekgeletak bage engo malot menawe nange Kane untuk memasti ken ise manusie edi kane tukhunlah salah sebuah pengawal mengato langsung te tekhyate Si Layakh lah si kalaki dapeti Napos ne me engah engah te deyat nadi ne se sikel-sikel bene te balik megekhot Kane ni babelah tubuh ne se engo geluh Si Layakh me Natam te ni dauni oleh tabit dukun mentakh
# text[en] = So, a small patrol from the Natam kingdom went to pursue King Ngkran's entourage. Right when they arrived at Pulo Biang they saw that in a chasm there was a human figure lying in it that looked lifeless. So to ascertain who the person was, one of the patrol men went down to take a look, and it turned out to be Si Layakh was the one that they found. He was breathing heavily and his pulse seemed to disappear and return again. So the body of the half-living Si Layakh was broght to Natam, and Tabib Tengku Putih tried to treat him.
# text[id] = Maka, menyusullah sekelompok kecil pengawal kerajaan Natam untuk menyusul rombongan Raja Ngkran.  Tepat saja sesampainya di Pulo Biang tampak dari bawah jurang sesosok manusia yang tergeletak sepertinya sudah tak bernyawa lagi.  Maka untuk memastikan siapa manusia itu maka turunlah salah-satu pengawal melihat langsung, dan ternyata Si Layakh lah yang mereka dapati.  Nafasnya ter-engah engah dan denyut nadinya seakan-akan hilang dan kembali berdetak.  Maka dibawalah tubuh setengah hidup Si Layakh ke Natam, dan di coba diobati oleh Tabib Tengku Putih.
