# text[en] = If a child has married household goods are given by the parents if their child is a son. If the son is already big then he is circumcised by his uncle's family. The one that is the uncle's family is from the uncle's side. His uncle uses a tray table and also uses a mattress, and uses a cow bone, and uses a chicken egg on the tray table. If he is already circumcised, the cultural ceremony njagai involves cooking sticky rice again. After that he returns to the mattress and also has cooked rice and vegetables with sticky rice.
# text[id] = Anak kalau udah nikah dipesulaki orangtuanya kalau ada anaknya anak laki-laki kalau sudah besar disunatkannya pakai pemamanen. yang pemamanen dari pihak pamannya. pamannya pakai pahar duduknya juga pakai kasur, pakai tulang lembu, pakai telur ayam dalam pahar itu. kalau sudah sunat di jagai pakai masak pulut lagi. setelah itu ngantarkan kasur juga pakai nasi dan sayur serta pulut.
