# text[en] = For life stories of husband and wife there are those that are happy, there are those that are full of suffering, there are those that are rich, there are those that are poor. there are those that are official, there are those that are not official, there are those that are jobless, there are those that have never been to school, there are some that have been to school, there are those which have parents who are able, and there are some with parents who are unable. How sad if the parents are unable to send us to school. Some parents who are able to send their children to school do not really want to, and just play around with school. Some kids have a big heart for school but their parents are not able to send them. Some love stories that have happened in this age. If this life is rich, officials value the people, to be disinclined. But if this life is poor, whatever his position is, he does not have a family and is not to be valued much by other people. People with a lot of wealth are the ones with the most happieness.
