# text = lot si ni pinang ni lajangi malet ingin anakhu kakhne nakhu e malet cinte padahal khang tue ne nggo mbelin ate ne me anak laki si mepangkat ge tapi anak ne malet cinte timbang timbang anakne ge kawin pagi khut khamah ne ge si kalak miskin lebih baik pakse khang tue ne ge me anak ne edi me kase sendah mbue terjadi anak sendah kawin mude salah pergaulen lebe ngo bebas su kawin segijap pul edi cekhe kakhene mange sange untuk mekhumah tangge lebe ngo hamil mange nikah pe sakit ne ate khangtue si nge lahekh ken ne edi kase sendah jage lah anak te mejile
# text[en] = There are those who are proposed to, there are those who are single, there are those who don't want a wife because they are not in love with anyone. Even though the parents have a big desire for a son who has status/work but the child does not have to love someone. Compared to a child that marries tomorrow with their boyfriend/girlfriend who is a poor person.  It is better to force the parents mentioned earlier with the child. That is so that now many child happen to marry easily as a result of wrong socialization. Some are already very free/loose. Married for a short time, after that divorced because it was not yet time to become a family. Some are already pregnant but are not yet married. The feelings of the parents of that child who had a baby are hurt.  It is true that now we have to protect our kids very well.
# text[id] = Ada yang dipinang, dilajangi, tidak mau anak perempuan karena anak perempuan itu tidak cinta  padahal orangtuanya udah besar hatinya dengan anak laki-laki yang punya pekerjaan tadi tapi anaknya tidak cinta daripada anaknya tadi kawin besok dengan pacarnya tadi yang orang miskin  lebih baik paksa orangtuanya tadi dengan anaknya  itulah supaya sekarang banyak terjadi anak sekarang nikah mudah salah pergaulan  sebagian sudah bebas kali nikah sebentar setelah itu cerai karena belum sampai untuk berumah tangga  sebagian sudah hamil belum nikah pun sakitnya hati orangtua yang melahirkannya  itulah sekarang jagalah anak kita bagus-bagus.
