# text = macam-macam usahe te petani mejagung mepage sawit coklat kakhet kembikhi galuh lade usahe kalak petani nde ndak wayang mbue ne modal ne nukokh khesep ne bibit ne apelagi jaman sendah nde pupuk pe malet daye lot pesen pupuk ndak wayang sekhik ne sekhik kalak petani ngeng ken se akibat pertambah daerah ne segale bakhang mahal
# text[en] = Our work is various types of farming. Planting corn, rice, chocolate, rubber, banana, and chili pepper (are some of the different kinds of farming). Their work as farmers is not a very big financial investment. They buy the prescribed seedlings. What's more in this age there is also fertilizer. Not selling there is to be ordered. Fertilizer is not very difficult. The difficulty for farmers is holding on to the result of their growing area. Everything is expensive.
# text[id] = Macam-macam usaha kita petani.  Berjagung, berpadi, sawit, coklat, karet, kemiri, pisang, cabe. Usaha mereka petani itu tidak sangat banyaknya modalnya. Beli resepnya bibitnya. Apalagi zaman kini ini pupuk pun. Bukan jual ada pesan.  Pupuk tidak sangat susahnya. Susah mereka petani tahankan seakhibat penambah daerahnya. Segala barang-benda mahal.
